author: Master_Wu
title: The Lord of Darkness on the go!
review:
For all of you Ninjago fans out there, I recommend this set!

Garmadon has got to be one of the coolest bad guys in all of Ninjago! And now you can get him on a keychain! I really enjoy being able to take him with me which is easy to do because you can attach him to your keys or backpack!

I recommend this set which you can get for a low price to take him with you wherever you go!
